---
// Process from brochure page 8
---

<section class="how-we-work section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>How We Help You Buy</h2>
      <p>Simple, transparent process from start to finish</p>
    </div>

    <div class="process-steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">1</div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Free Consultation</h3>
        <p>We learn about your needs, budget, and timeline through a detailed property brief</p>
        <p class="step-note">No obligation, no pressure</p>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">2</div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"></path>
            <polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"></polyline>
            <line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"></line>
            <line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"></line>
            <polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Define Your Criteria</h3>
        <p>Budget, location, property type, and must-haves</p>
        <p class="step-note">We create your customized property brief</p>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">3</div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"></circle>
            <path d="m21 21-4.35-4.35"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Diligent Research & Sourcing</h3>
        <p>We search on-market AND off-market properties across Queensland</p>
        <p class="step-note">Access to exclusive deals you won't find online - we review 40+ properties weekly</p>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">4</div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M9 11l3 3L22 4"></path>
            <path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Inspections & Due Diligence</h3>
        <p>We meticulously shortlist properties and attend inspections on your behalf</p>
        <p class="step-note">Complete due diligence: building & pest inspections, flood reports, council regulations</p>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">5</div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Strategic Negotiation</h3>
        <p>We negotiate on your behalf using our deep agent relationships</p>
        <p class="step-note">Real estate agents give our clients preference—they know deals won't fall through</p>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">6</div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="m3 9 9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"></path>
            <polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Settlement Support</h3>
        <p>We provide unwavering support through settlement proceedings</p>
        <p class="step-note">Final inspection, seamless handover—you move into your dream property</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Fee Transparency -->
    <div class="fee-transparency">
      <div class="fee-content">
        <h3>Our Service Fees</h3>
        <p class="fee-intro">At Edwards & Smith, transparency is paramount. We offer a flat fee structure with no hidden costs.</p>

        <div class="fee-details">
          <div class="fee-item">
            <h4>Queensland (Brisbane & Gold Coast)</h4>
            <p class="fee-amount">Typically 2-3% of purchase price</p>
          </div>
          <div class="fee-item">
            <h4>Bali, Indonesia</h4>
            <p class="fee-amount">Under 5% of purchase price</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fee-includes">
          <h4>What's Included:</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Full property search (40+ properties reviewed weekly)</li>
            <li>All inspections and due diligence</li>
            <li>Expert negotiation on your behalf</li>
            <li>Complete settlement support</li>
            <li>No timeframe pressure—we take as long as needed</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p class="fee-note">Our fees are determined by the overall purchase price of the property, ensuring fairness and clarity. Unlike other services, we don't operate within strict timeframes—whether the search takes three weeks or three months, our commitment remains unwavering.</p>

        <div class="cta-center">
          <a href="/consultation" class="button-primary">Get a Custom Quote</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .how-we-work {
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 70px;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .section-header p {
    font-size: var(--body-large);
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  .process-steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .step {
    background-color: var(--white);
    padding: 35px 30px;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-small);
    box-shadow: var(--box-shadow-subtle);
    position: relative;
  }

  .step-number {
    position: absolute;
    top: -15px;
    left: 30px;
    background-color: var(--primary-green);
    color: var(--white);
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .step-icon {
    color: var(--primary-green);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }

  .step h3 {
    color: var(--primary-green);
    font-size: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .step p {
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .step-note {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-light);
    font-style: italic;
    background-color: #f5f5f5;
    padding: 10px 15px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--primary-green);
  }

  .fee-transparency {
    background-color: var(--white);
    padding: 60px;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-small);
    box-shadow: var(--box-shadow-subtle);
  }

  .fee-content h3 {
    color: var(--primary-green);
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .fee-intro {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: var(--body-large);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .fee-details {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 30px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .fee-item {
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
    padding: 30px;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-small);
    text-align: center;
    border-top: 3px solid var(--primary-green);
  }

  .fee-item h4 {
    color: var(--primary-green);
    font-size: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .fee-amount {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .fee-includes {
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
    padding: 30px;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-small);
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .fee-includes h4 {
    color: var(--primary-green);
    font-size: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .fee-includes ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .fee-includes li {
    padding-left: 28px;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .fee-includes li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--primary-green);
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 18px;
  }

  .fee-note {
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-center {
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .process-steps {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .fee-details {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .fee-transparency {
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .process-steps {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
